OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOften rather cloudy but bright
OL,6,For sunny spells developing through the
OL,7,Fmorning, and still feeling pleasantly
OL,8,Fwarm. Scattered heavy showers may
OL,9,Fdevelop into the afternoon, towards
OL,10,Fthe south, with a chance of thunder.
OL,11,FWinds generally light.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowers in the south fading
OL,14,Fas overcast conditions extend
OL,15,Fsouthwards, with areas of low cloud
OL,16,Fand the odd spot of drizzle. Light
OL,17,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
