OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FGradually turning brighter and
OL,6,Fa little cooler from the north. Mostly
OL,7,Fdry, although a few mostly light
OL,8,Fshowers are still possible. Winds
OL,9,Fremaining generally light.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FBright
OL,12,For sunny spells and a chance of
OL,13,Fshowers each day, these perhaps more
OL,14,Flikely Tuesday. Turning cooler, with
OL,15,Fovernight rural frost possible in
OL,16,Fsheltered spots. Winds mostly light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
